*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aʊz|-aʊz]]
===Noun===
'''blouse''' (''plural:'' '''blouses''')
#an [[outer]] [[garment]], usually [[loose]], that is similar to a [[shirt]] and reaches from the [[neck]] to the [[waist]] or below. Nowadays, in colloquial use, ''blouse'' refers almost always to a woman's garment.
